<div id="zx">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero" id="zxhero">
    <div class="hero-copy reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">The Serenity Set · Acupressure ritual</span>
      <h1>Twenty quiet minutes,<br>and the day <em>lets go</em>.</h1>
      <p class="lead">An acupressure mat and contoured neck pillow, made for the slow minutes between the day and sleep — where tension in the neck, shoulders and back finally softens.</p>
      <div class="hero-price">
        <span class="now">$49.99</span>
        <span class="was">$99.99</span>
        <span class="note">· Introductory price, first edition</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="{{ purl }}" class="btn btn-primary">Begin the ritual <svg class="ico sm arr" style="stroke:currentColor"><use href="#zxi-arrow"></use></svg></a>
        <p class="reassure">60-night money-back trial · Free US shipping</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-trust">
        <span><svg class="ico sm"><use href="#zxi-leaf"></use></svg> Drug-free</span>
        <span><svg class="ico sm"><use href="#zxi-shield"></use></svg> 60-night trial</span>
        <span><svg class="ico sm"><use href="#zxi-truck"></use></svg> Free US shipping</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-media reveal">
      <img src="{{ img }}pexels-photo-6453915.jpg?v=1782829005&amp;width=1100" alt="A woman resting calmly in soft morning light" width="1100" height="1375" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" decoding="async">
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TRUST STRIP -->
  <section class="strip">
    <div class="wrap">
      <span><svg class="ico sm"><use href="#zxi-truck"></use></svg> Free US shipping over $50</span>
      <span><svg class="ico sm"><use href="#zxi-shield"></use></svg> 60-night money-back trial</span>
      <span><svg class="ico sm"><use href="#zxi-lock"></use></svg> Secure checkout</span>
      <span><svg class="ico sm"><use href="#zxi-leaf"></use></svg> Ships from the US</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- RITUAL / MANIFESTO -->
  <section class="ritual">
    <div class="inner reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow center">The ritual</span>
      <p>Lie down. Let the points meet your skin. Breathe until the day loosens its grip. Twenty minutes — the same length as the scroll you won't miss.</p>
      <div class="rule"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROBLEM BAND -->
  <section class="band">
    <div class="band-media reveal">
      <img src="{{ img }}pexels-photo-3822622.jpg?v=1782829094&amp;width=900" alt="A woman easing tension in her neck and shoulders" width="900" height="1125" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
    </div>
    <div class="band-copy reveal d1">
      <span class="eyebrow">The evening you know</span>
      <h2>You carry the day in your shoulders.</h2>
      <p class="lead">A tight neck. A mind still running. The body braced long after the work is done.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:18px">The Serenity Set gives all of it somewhere to land — a few honest minutes that tell the nervous system it's finally safe to rest.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT IT GIVES -->
  <section class="gives">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow center">What the ritual gives back</span>
      <h2>A better off-switch for your evenings</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="gives-list">
      <div class="give reveal">
        <div class="ic"><svg class="ico"><use href="#zxi-moon"></use></svg></div>
        <div><h3>A quieter mind</h3><p>Lie back, breathe, and let the day downshift. Often the simple cue to be still is all the body needs to begin letting go.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="give reveal d1">
        <div class="ic"><svg class="ico"><use href="#zxi-release"></use></svg></div>
        <div><h3>Neck &amp; shoulders, released</h3><p>Thousands of contact points press evenly across the back, while the contoured pillow reaches the curve a flat mat can't.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="give reveal d2">
        <div class="ic"><svg class="ico"><use href="#zxi-rest"></use></svg></div>
        <div><h3>An easier evening</h3><p>A calm wind-down to mark the end of the day — no screen, no pill, nothing to charge. A practice you return to.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STEPS -->
  <section class="steps-sec">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow center">How it works</span>
      <h2>Three steps to calm, tonight</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step reveal"><div class="num">01</div><div class="br"></div><h3>Unroll it</h3><p>Lay the mat where you rest — bed, couch or floor — and set the pillow beneath your neck.</p></div>
      <div class="step reveal d1"><div class="num">02</div><div class="br"></div><h3>Lie back</h3><p>A few minutes of sharp, bright warmth, then a spreading ease as the muscles settle.</p></div>
      <div class="step reveal d2"><div class="num">03</div><div class="br"></div><h3>Let go</h3><p>Stay twenty minutes, most evenings. The practice does the rest — many drift off before it's done.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FULL-BLEED LIFESTYLE -->
  <section class="bleed reveal">
    <img src="{{ img }}pexels-photo-7445026.jpg?v=1782829008&amp;width=1700" alt="A calm, candlelit bedroom in the evening" width="1700" height="1133" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
    <div class="bc">
